  <brief_title>Study of 5 and 10 Days Treatment With Penicillin Against Sore Throat Caused by Streptococci</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Controlled Study of 5 and 10 Days Treatment With Phenoxymethylpenicillin for Pharyngotonsillitis Caused by Streptococcus Group A</official_title>
  <sponsors>
