  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Clinical cure</measure>
    <time_frame>5-7 days after discontinuation of treatment</time_frame>
    <description>Difference between treatment groups in the rate of clinical cure. Clinical cure is defined as clinical judgement by physician and absence of Centor criteria (coating, fever and swollen Large Granular Lymphocyte glands).</description>
  </primary_outcome>
